high_descs: Turn right for two steps, turn left and stop at the counter.
Pick up the cup, with a fork stuck through its side, on the upper right corner of the counter.
Turn right for two steps, turn left and stop in front of the stove.
Open the microwave door, put the cup in the microwave with the handle of the fork pointing left then shut the door. Wait a few seconds and open the door, take the cup out and shut the door.
Turn right for one step and hold the cup up.
Open the upper cabinet door, put the cup in the cabinet then shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup, with a fork stuck through its side, in an upper cabinet.

high_descs: Take a step right, and then walk forward to the counter on the left of the stove.
Pick up the gray cup on the counter.
Heat the cup in the microwave.
Place the cup in the big cabinet above the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated cup in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the counter between the refrigerator and stove.
Pick up the bowl that is behind the tomato.
Walk to the right to the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the bowl inside, close the microwave. Open the microwave, remove the bowl, close the microwave.
Turn to the right and walk to the cabinet to the right of the sink and beside the window.
Place the bowl into the cabinet to the left of the cabinet by the window.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm bowl into a cabinet.
